description: Spectacular 3 bed, 2.5 bath penthouse with a 900 sq ft private roof deck offering stunning city views! This light-filled home features soaring ceilings, oversized windows, and hardwood floors throughout. The chef’s kitchen is equipped with marble countertops, a Bertazzoni 5-burner stove, beverage cooler, and ample storage. Two of the three bedrooms offer en-suite baths, and all have excellent closets. Additional features include in-unit laundry, an oversized pantry, garage parking, and a private storage closet. The expansive roof deck is perfect for relaxing, grilling, and entertaining. Located just two blocks from the West Broadway T station, one block from Flaherty Park playground, and close to Southie beaches, major highways, restaurants, and shops—this home offers the best of city living.
